### Additional Notes for Portfolio Usage:

- You are free to:
  - Use this as a template for your personal/company portfolio
  - Modify colors, content, and structure
  - Deploy your modified version publicly

- You should:
  - Replace all personal information (name, projects, contact details) with your own
  - Consider changing the visual design to make it uniquely yours
  - Update the theme system if keeping the multi-theme functionality

- You may not:
  - Redistribute the original or modified versions as a "portfolio template" for sale
  - Use the design for commercial projects unrelated to personal portfolio use

